cdata.name: Dataeum
cdata.desc:
Dataeum is aBlockchain-based collaborative platform for physical data generation. Itsprimary objective is to create an ecosystem where users can gather physical data(fromstores, gas stations, traffic signs, etc) and then make it availablein a decentralized marketplace, trough the platform's app. Datareumexpects to be successful in gathering 100% of the physical data in the world.

The XDT token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by the Dataeum. It is the token that will serveas a medium of exchange value within the platform and can berelated to Data collection, Data licensing, Merchants interaction,as well as other Dataeum supported services.
